text: An Vannieuwenhuyse (born 3 March 1991) is a Belgian bobsledder. She competed in the two-woman event at the 2018 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1991 births Category:Living people Category:Belgian female bobsledders Category:Olympic bobsledders of Belgium Category:Bobsledders at the 2018 Winter Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
